resources.string:
Málaga Club de Fútbol,founded in 1948, 
is a symbol of passion and dedication for our fans. 
Over the years, we have faced challenges and achieved 
significant achievements both in the Spanish League and in European 
competitions With optimism and ambition, we continue to grow and reach new goals, being a 
source of pride for Málaga and Andalusia. Our fans are the essence of Málaga CF. With their unconditional support, they transform each La Rosaleda match into a party of colors and emotions. The relationship with our fans is close and authentic, they are the heart and soul that drive our team.
